column5: Anybody have any info on the Pike derby on cooks bay out of Pacedina Marina its usually this weekend coming or the next I believe its Aurora BassMasters that put it on but i cant get anything off their site I dont want to miss it Turkey has been a bust and missing this will put me over the side for sure  Cheers Peter
Dang... and here I thought this was about you trying to get your crayola cup back !!!

Looks like it will be on the long weekend (may 22) $110 a team.  hard to find because it is written in the middle of a big paragraph on the tourny page.  Email Tom Tsatskas for more details.  [emailÂ protected]   Need a partner?
